{"id":430,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":32,"title":"32. Bus Stop","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":20,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/32-bus-stop.430/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/32-bus-stop-2022-03-07-21-14-34/0-32-bus-stop.mp3","transcript":"Jean!\nBarbara! Do you work around here?\nYes, I work in that building across the street.\nReally? What do you do?\nI work in a law office, I'm a secretary.\nOh, that's interesting.\nWhat about you? What do you do?\nI work at Duru Restaurant.\nOh... are you a cook?\nNo, I'm a waitress.\nThat's a really hard job; I don't envy you.\nMe neither!\nDo you live alone, Jean?\nNo, I don't. I live with my family. How about you?\nI'm married now. I got married last year.\nReally? Congratulations! Who did you marry?\nHis name's Jeff Hunt. He lives in my building.\nOh, what does he do?\nHe's a doctor.\nHow wonderful, I'm very happy for you!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:38","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Jean!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/32-bus-stop-2022-03-07-21-14-34/1.mp3","time_start":2.19,"time_end":2.97},{"position":2,"content":"Barbara! Do you work around here?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/32-bus-stop-2022-03-07-21-14-34/2.mp3","time_start":2.97,"time_end":4.74},{"position":3,"content":"Yes, I work in that building across the street.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/32-bus-stop-2022-03-07-21-14-34/3.mp3","time_start":4.74,"time_end":7.22},{"position":4,"content":"Really? What do you do?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/32-bus-stop-2022-03-07-21-14-34/4.mp3","time_start":7.18,"time_end":8.48},{"position":5,"content":"I work in a law office, I'm a secretary.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com